{"tid":1152102,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"領先7分，猁狗串過馬撚","createTime":"2019-05-12T17:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T07:27:36.000Z","uid":9347,"like":328,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"72d842d36ba06d48965b94e8ef4e87c2fc23abd4","tid":1152102,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"領先7分，猁狗串過馬撚<br />\n領先2分，猁狗平常心面對<br />\n領先收窄至1分，聯賽爭標汲汲可危，猁狗要求愛華頓放水，以爭取馬西塞特郡光榮<br />\n落後1分，聯賽俾反超前，高普俾人屌老母，沙拿變非洲狗<br />\n史上最高分亞軍<br />\n拉莫斯：我老母終於有得抖下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20561f78eb19a2a3a955a929a530f2d38395a2da","tid":1152102,"uid":9347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f036b436c3e457349ebcf51000c5e612d921541d","tid":1152102,"uid":65062,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:51:10.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"9550ce93a467563ff15f130ffd891dbb5c770eb0","tid":1152102,"uid":9347,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:52:05.000Z","msg":"等歐聯完咗又要再作多句<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498b3991957e431f46a7a6c0cd465254cff5f17c","tid":1152102,"uid":59931,"like":61,"dislike":8,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:58:16.000Z","msg":"講咁耐 不如搵番季初至聖誕話串柒柒既po出黎<br />\n永遠得個講字無prove既屌"},{"pid":"4a2c80babd190054652e3413c4a64f02c9051f62","tid":1152102,"uid":74452,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:19:06.000Z","msg":"個撚個都話串柒柒<br />\nCap張圖黎睇下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf2683324ed2be89f2dab47862f8bc46135dc29","tid":1152102,"